data.description: Located on a corner lot in the Carriage House Village subdivision, this three-bedroom, two-bathroom brick home offers everything you want and more! The living room features a fireplace, and the open floorplan is great for entertaining. The spacious kitchen is the hallmark of the home. The master suite wouldn't be complete without a high ceilings in the bedroom and a bathroom with double vanity and separate shower/soaking tub! Natural light is abundant throughout the home, thanks to several large, energy-efficient windows. Enjoy summer days in your privacy-fenced backyard or walk down to the community pool or park. Belton ISD With all that this home has to offer, it won't last long! Make it yours today!
